{"type": "article", "id": 23522, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考，并且综合了包括技术、商业在内的多种力量。我们希望持续关注这些变化，它是美好生活的动力之一。", "date": "2016-03-09T07:30:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 1954, "name": "包装"}, {"id": 23565, "name": "Fogia"}, {"id": 24608, "name": "Panta Rei"}, {"id": 24609, "name": "WorkOf"}, {"id": 24610, "name": "Souda"}, {"id": 24611, "name": "Stefan Borselius"}, {"id": 24612, "name": "Shima Jahani"}, {"id": 24613, "name": "Kate Casey"}, {"id": 24614, "name": "Marco Vincit"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 40, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702110333T7NZhrBtMm1Uc0bf.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p>\n<h2>Campo sofa by Stefan Borselius &amp; Fogia</h2>\n<p>这组沙发来自瑞典设计师 Stefan Borseliu 和瑞典家具品牌 Fogia，扶手是椭圆形的，靠垫和坐垫都近似于厚实的枕头，给人柔和舒适的感受。支撑沙发的结构是细的橡木腿，以衬托出沙发的宽阔。设计师称形状的灵感源于梵蒂冈的坎波广场 （Piazza del Campo)，大概是因为广场带给人的典雅和温暖。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153634sTq3Ebk62K8PNgiw.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153635YS3pxqycvPuUVaQG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54487179\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153635SNx9da1kDFEpJUyo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77350427\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071536362RqHg5V4nQlusBpf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153636rvzmZC7yc8tnKlf6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Panta Rei Light Cube </h2>\n<p>这盏方盒子一样的桌灯有一个层层变小的“洞”，它是用纸板做的，自动让光线有了层次感。从前到后滑动上面的 LED 光源时，能看到流动的光影，非常炫目。灯的造型本身具有雕塑感，流动的光影却像是现代的霓虹灯，有了另一种结合。有多位设计师参与，他们称这盏灯符合苏格拉底的名言一切都在流动中。<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/32910829/Light-Cube-Panta-Rei\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153636TU2hiOcC64Ab3Peo.gif\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153637XZ4OpIMKQBAHqd0E.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153638FwxKd4OmgjBhzsEi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153638n91BALylYWETh7Fw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071536398CI09oXyBjO1T5tx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>STRUT SHELVING SYSTEM by WorkOf &amp; Souda</h2>\n<p>这个书架来自纽约布鲁克林的工作室 Souda，由一家线上设计网站 WorkOf 出售。它使用金属三脚架做支撑固定在墙上，一块浅色的木板横亘在其中，恰好在中间的位置，使得书架维持了中心对称。因为模块化的设计，可以在墙上排列多个架子构成一面书架，很灵活。有 6 种颜色和 3 种材料的木板可选，售价 350 美元起，<a href=\"http://workof.com/p/strut-shelving-system-copper/\">这里是购买链接。</a></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153640z4rWpUhHfs6d9yMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153640pVeYwuqILjQ546Ea.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153640sgn3wYdW9vf7N5Tj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153642QhUFM96g8lwzVrcv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153642RbNhuk0wX618JlOf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>outdoor object by Shima Jahani</h2>\n<p>这是一个放在公共场所的设施，结合了桌椅、垃圾桶和自行车停放架。设计师利用废弃的铁架和木材，将它们整合成屏风一样的装置里，是连贯的。放在大树下面有保护树木的作用，也能成为一个景观。产品目前还是概念，但提供一种重新思考公共设施设计的角度。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153643hdyVJgoP43CMQan5.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.69142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153643tFO8u03MKdBvsx7L.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70952381\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153644z5KvdgVFm27lspLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65142857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153644Nxy5lZ9mzUfknD0O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>Peg Woodworking by Kate Casey</h2>\n<p>这套编织家具来自纽约女设计师 Kate Casey，她成立了独立工作室 PEG WOODWORKING。座位和椅背上是她自己用棉线手工编织的图案，经过交叉和重叠之后形成了丰富的几何图形。有些通过不同颜色做区分，有些仅仅依靠疏密表现了深浅和光泽。这是设计师的工作室和<a href=\"http://www.pegwoodworking.com/new-products/\">购买链接</a>。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153645suw9r6mMgdhLeTfy.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153646hgaWLzVyOSf19ok4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153646BL43YzZ5DePs7kvi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153647Clr6pJz0DLAWXhtn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016060715364772iCrhUxB13w6you.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49833333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<h2>VINCIT BEER SPECIAL LIMITED EDITION by Marco Vincit</h2>\n<p>这是一款啤酒的特别版包装，主要采用了白黄相间的圆点图案，清新而亮丽。酒瓶是传统的棕色半透明的琥珀瓶，白色的贴纸上出现了黄色半圆形图案和图案作为底色，从正面看，文字和图案又配合成了一个娃娃的笑脸，黑色的 VINCIT 像是眼睛，图标作为鼻子，下面也有一串细长的弧形文字作为嘴巴，很俏皮。另外，配合这套啤酒包装拍摄的宣传图也很漂亮。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153648Ix4RjMYBcOaSvw3n.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153648PaQfv54gZHF0kemw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153649PeKarRvytiCLNVU8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071536498oCYA1EfPvzyguLa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153650NzxQanIA6BDYSGWm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607153651HgWGZACbP5frRjVB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n"}